name: PROPERTIES 03 - House in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. 
This spacious property is ideal for a group of friends or a couple of tots. 
It is made up of 3 bright rooms in addition to a balcony that invites you to enjoy chats under the starry night. 
The lower floor has a unique environment. Is arranged as a meeting area that maintains a space to invite approximately 30 humans and/or cat friends. 
Land measurements: 60m x 70m
